<h2>Malawi</h2>

<img src="mwflag1964.png" alt="" width="450" height="300">

<p><small>Source: <a href="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/d/d1/Flag_of_Malawi.svg">Wiki Commons</a></small></p>

<p>This flag was used from independence (1964) to 2010, when a revised form

was adopted (see below). The change was however generaaly unpopular, and was

reversed in 2012.</p>





<p><small>2010-12 flag: (Source: <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Flag_of_Malawi_(2010-2012).svg">Wiki Commons</a>)</small><br>

<img src="mwflag2010.png" alt="Malawi flag, 2010-12" height="84" width="125"></p>





